.DS_Store

# Collected and generated data stay local. Only directory placeholders are tracked.
data/**
!data/**/
!data/**/.gitkeep
!data/README.md
logs/*
artifacts/**
!artifacts/**/
!artifacts/**/.gitkeep
!artifacts/README.md

# Keep directory placeholders.
!logs/.gitkeep

# Local notes and work log (not for remote).
docs/MENTORING_GUIDE.md
docs/WORK_LOG.md
docs/PROJECT_PROPOSAL.md

# Local Codex work tracker and lifecycle automation (never publish).
/AGENTS.md
/.codex/
/docs/WORK_TRACKER.md
/docs/work_tracker.json
/scripts/work_tracker_hook.py
/src/open_fiscal_pipeline/work_tracker.py
/tests/test_work_tracker.py
